snippet.title: Warstu
snippet.description:
Welcome to the The Warstu Channel, run by me, I aim to bring you the best quality content when it comes to Marvel And DC,
We cover the following Marvel,Avengers Endgame, Marvel Phase 4 5, Spider-Man No Way Home, Captain Marvel, Doctor Strange, Fantastic Four, X-Men,Venom, BATFLECK, Justice League, Zack Snyder Justice League, Snyderverse, DCEU Superman, Wonder Woman, The Flash, Aquaman, Godzilla Vs Kong, The Witcher and many others.

We cover these in a wide range of content News, theories, reviews, breaking news, comic con panels, Set photos, Plot Leaks, Fan plot leaks trailer breakdowns, and much more.

Warstu channel has been featured multiple times on global websites such as Dailymail.co.uk, Mens Health Uk, Independent, IGN. & Comicbook.com amongst many others. 

Follow my Socials 
Instagram @warstu
Twitter @warstuG
